Class FlipFitGymCustomerBusiness

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.FlipFitGymCustomerBusiness
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFlipFitGymCustomer
public class FlipFitGymCustomerBusiness extends Object implements IFlipFitGymCustomer
Business logic for managing FlipFit Gym customer operations. Implements functionality for viewing bookings, checking conflicts, editing customer details, and managing payment and registration.
